{"tid":1928591,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"康文署：23人兩度入住檢疫中心 其中一人3度入住","createTime":"2020-03-16T13:09:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-16T15:04:37.000Z","uid":212626,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"34a3374822c2208684ea6f536742e4098d759e07","tid":1928591,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T13:09:16.000Z","msg":"康文署說，入住政府提供暫住設施作強制檢疫的人士，相信有五分一個案涉及懷疑濫用。明日起，政府會向入住人士，每人每日收取200元作入住及膳食收費。康文署回覆查詢時說，<span style=\"color: red;\">發現23人完成第一次強制檢疫令後再次入住暫住設施，其中一人已是第3次入住。另有超過130個在港有其他居所的人士，堅持入住暫住設施，部分人士表明為了免費食宿</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">中心職員又曾在檢疫人士離營後，發現營內的物品如電線拖板、風筒、淋浴露及電子探熱針等被人私自取走，又觀察到有離營人士攜走大量政府發放的食物，如杯麵等</span>。<br />\n<br />\n康文署說，如受檢疫人士未能繳付有關費用，政府會向有關人士追討，亦可能影響受檢疫人士將來使用政府部分設施和服務的權利。假若受檢疫人士無視政府欠款追討通知，當局有權採取法律行動。若因經濟問題未能繳交費用，政府會個別考慮每宗個案，決定會否豁免收費或提供其他協助。<br />\n<br />\n由上月8日凌晨起，衞生署要求從內地入境人士，必須強制在家居或其他住所接受隔離檢疫14天。若香港居民在本港無法安排入住地方，則將由政府安排入住暫住設施，即曹公潭戶外康樂中心、西貢戶外康樂中心或麥理浩夫人度假村，進行檢疫。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1514842-20200316.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1514842-20200316.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=eokTwrWYlXUgHXHl4H%2Bebc0oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=74422f03\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1514842-20200316.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=df61e9bf\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1514842-20200316.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"3a5ce566519d005d3bb42fbb83a4e7d2ed588ecf","tid":1928591,"uid":77717,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T13:11:19.000Z","msg":"支那人貪小便宜心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06cebd7462afca5b44cf39b46e28627f64c826cc","tid":1928591,"uid":212626,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T13:11:21.000Z","msg":"另有超過130個在港有其他居所的人士，堅持入住暫住設施，部分人士表明為了免費食宿<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d797ab081bd464d8a6bbb25acb2d62151d41a046","tid":1928591,"uid":63154,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T13:11:50.000Z","msg":"證明頻密往返中港都必然唔會係咩好人"},{"pid":"8fb250c0b39b1e97d436823836510f5c32cd3767","tid":1928591,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T13:13:15.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"b67fcebd7b579495a71b1773882f1a1cdecac401","tid":1928591,"uid":297241,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T13:14:43.000Z","msg":"搵度假村做隔離營, 最後又係變咗度假村<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcbb99e7b25e484d0d2ced2e397b2aaa7227bc8a","tid":1928591,"uid":275588,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T13:15:27.000Z","msg":"係人都諗到會白食白住<br />\n係政府諗唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0725cc58e8fa31cae3825234b1efcfa39f4e13d","tid":1928591,"uid":107681,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T13:16:17.000Z","msg":"有免費野d廢老點會放過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n班撚樣燃燒生命黎r著數"},{"pid":"58d0f26d4b40a0e57562378427f3472441790552","tid":1928591,"uid":350216,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T13:21:56.000Z","msg":"應該係連登發起逼爆政府......隔離中心行動，社會癱瘓指日可待<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n兩袋肥牛，thanks"},{"pid":"088b17de593451860000b0e9619e6a668caeb7c6","tid":1928591,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T13:26:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bde73b6eb26016416fc30e8779beed3a9cc31c37","tid":1928591,"uid":63154,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b0725cc58e8fa31cae3825234b1efcfa39f4e13d","tid":1928